annotationA: Importin subunit alpha; Protein transmembrane transporter activity. It is involved in the biological process described with: protein import into nucleus; proteasome assembly; Belongs to the importin alpha family
annotationB: Exportin-2; Export receptor for importin alpha. Mediates importin- alpha re-export from the nucleus to the cytoplasm after import substrates have been released into the nucleoplasm (By similarity)
